---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const phone = '(352) 292-1499';
const phoneTel = '3522921499';
const city = 'Hudson';
const county = 'Pasco County';
---

<Layout 
  title={`Concrete Contractors in ${city}, FL | Driveways, Patios & Slabs`}
  description={`Trusted concrete contractors in ${city}, Florida. Quality driveways, patios, slabs, and coastal concrete for Pasco County. Call ${phone}!`}
  canonical="/locations/hudson/"
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Concrete Contractors in {city}, Florida</h1>
      <p>Professional concrete installation for {city} properties. Quality work from experienced Nature Coast contractors.</p>
      <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {phone}</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>Concrete Services for {city} Residents</h2>
          <p>{city} sits along Florida's Gulf coast in northern Pasco County, offering residents a relaxed coastal lifestyle with convenient access to both nature and amenities. The community includes waterfront properties, established inland neighborhoods, and growing residential areas—each with specific concrete needs.</p>
          
          <p>Brooksville Concrete Co. extends our services south into Hudson, bringing the same expertise and quality we're known for in Hernando County. Our experience with coastal conditions—something Hudson shares with our Hernando Beach service area—means we understand what it takes to build concrete that lasts in a coastal environment.</p>
          
          <p>From driveway replacements to new patios, from pool decks to workshop slabs, we provide comprehensive concrete services throughout Hudson and surrounding areas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h3>{city} Concrete Services</h3>
          <ul class="why-list">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Coastal Driveways</strong>
                Driveways built to handle salt air and coastal conditions common in Hudson.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Patios & Pool Decks</strong>
                Outdoor living spaces with slip-resistant, attractive finishes.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Waterfront Concrete</strong>
                Specialized solutions for Gulf-front and canal properties.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Slabs & Foundations</strong>
                Solid foundations for sheds, workshops, and outbuildings.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-content">
    <h2>Coastal Concrete Expertise for {city}</h2>
    
    <p>Hudson's Gulf coast location creates specific challenges for concrete work. Salt air accelerates deterioration, high water tables affect installation methods, and flood zone considerations come into play for many properties. Our experience with similar conditions throughout the Nature Coast means we understand how to address these challenges.</p>

    <h3>Building for Coastal Conditions</h3>
    
    <p>For Hudson projects, we employ techniques developed through years of coastal concrete work:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Salt-resistant formulations:</strong> Concrete mixes designed to resist salt damage</li>
      <li><strong>Quality sealers:</strong> Protection against moisture and salt penetration</li>
      <li><strong>Proper drainage:</strong> Grading and design that manages water effectively</li>
      <li><strong>Appropriate reinforcement:</strong> Steel placement that accounts for coastal soil conditions</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Residential Services in {city}</h3>
    
    <p>Most of our Hudson work involves residential properties. We help homeowners with driveway replacement—whether upgrading an older surface or installing new construction; patio installation—creating outdoor living spaces perfect for enjoying Gulf breezes; pool deck work—slip-resistant, cool surfaces around your pool; and walkways—connecting your home to outdoor areas and other structures.</p>

    <h3>Quality You Can Count On</h3>
    
    <p>Every Hudson project uses premium materials: 4,000+ PSI concrete, fiber reinforcement, and quality sealers. We don't compromise on materials, and our experienced crews don't compromise on installation. The result is concrete that looks great and performs well for years to come.</p>
    
    <p>Contact Brooksville Concrete Co. for your free Hudson estimate. Call <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>{phone}</a> or complete our online form to get started.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Coastal Concrete Experts for {city}</h2>
      <p>Quality concrete built for Gulf coast conditions</p>
      <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`} class="btn">Call {phone} Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
